s and propose several ideas for improvement such as\ncontrolling frequency components, using different wavelets and using other\nstate-of-the-art NF architectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Mar 2021 16:47:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-24"}
